I usually take my front loader NES apart if I want to use the gyromite adapter. Famicom games won't really fit in there otherwise.<br /><br />As an adapter though I think it's good, and the board is accessible so it's easy to modify. I added an extra wire for the audio expansions.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5165">rainwarrior</a> — Thu Jan 16, 2014 8:50 pm</p><hr />
